summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 25000 entitled: "An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for improvement of Western Avenue from Seneca Street to Denny Way, et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading, etc., under Ordinance No. 21703 creating Local Improvement District No. 2159, prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement."
